snippet.title: Namco Super Wars (ナムコスーパーウォーズ) - WonderSwan Color gameplay sample
snippet.description:
Seems like a neat SRPG for the shortlived WonderSwan (Color). A pretty cool thing is that you can choose your weapon even during the enemy's turn.
I could barely find other gameplay videos on YouTube of this game, and these were really short, so I thought that I should record it myself. Also, there's not a lot of information about this game online. Strange considering that this is a Namco game.
